title: The Hungry Hippo
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A late night, board game cafe. Vegan choices are marked on the menu and include fries, sweet potato chips, falafel with tahini dipping sauce, beer battered deep fried pickles, baked swiss mushrooms brushed with pesto, tempura veggies with dipping sauce, salads, vegan milkshakes. Costs is $5 per person to play games. 3 hours is allocated to each group.
